				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Vignette AD for the Flaming Fist in the entrance hall of Wyrm's Rock in Wyrm's Crossing.\r\nVignette summary:\r\n\"People are going back and forth on an hourly basis usually. We should still see traces of Flaming Fists coming and going, as well as show the omnipresence of the Steel Watchers and other security systems (inert traps from Gortash’s boss fight that activate only if you attack him at the ceremony would be great).\""
				}
			}
